# AI Developer 👨‍💻⚡

AI Developer is a full-stack, real-time collaborative coding platform built using the MERN stack, enhanced with AI-powered features via Google Gemini. It allows users to create projects, collaborate with friends, chat in real time, and request AI assistance for code generation and review — all within a sleek, modern UI.

---

## 🚀 Features

- 🧠 **AI Code Assistant**: Use `@ai` in chat to get code suggestions or answers via Gemini AI.
- 📂 **Project Management**: Create and manage projects individually or with teammates.
- 💬 **Real-time Chat**: Chat with friends using Socket.io — updates are instant.
- 👥 **Friend System**: Add other registered users to your projects.
- 📄 **Code Review**: Paste code into the review tool to receive AI-generated suggestions.
- 🌙 **Dark Mode**: Enjoy a modern dark-themed interface.
- 🧱 **MVC Architecture**: Cleanly organized backend and frontend code structure.

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

### Frontend:
- React
- Tailwind CSS v3
- Vite
- Socket.io-client

### Backend:
- Node.js
- Express.js
- MongoDB
- Redis (Session & Caching)
- Socket.io
- Google Gemini API
- JWT (Authentication)

